    "Pinned OCI SDK contract: CreateApmDomain, GetApmDomain, ListApmDomains, ChangeApmDomainCompartment, UpdateApmDomain, DeleteApmDomain, and GetWorkRequest are present in v65.110.0. ListApmDomains filters compartmentId, displayName, and lifecycleState, while create, update, and delete responses expose opc-work-request-id but do not return an ApmDomain body.",
